metadata.name: i see
metadata.description:
the beauty,    
with my eyes wide open    
i can be there  
with my imagination   
 i am there    
how i feel the beauty    
is yet to be known   
 we only have five senses    
that do so much    
only with the fact    
that emotions betray us   
 love blinds us   
 fear takes control     
can you see fear?   
no,   
 i want to be   
no more  
than just me  
 why do i have to fight    
the world and my senses  
 for me,    
why can’t they leave me be    
to feel alive is a commodity    
nowadays
